Logistics and Construction Specialist - Abu Dhabi - 4 Month contract - Immediate requirement.
Working in Abu Dhabi you will be a specialist on a project to design the logistics of infrastructure, accommodation and facilities of a 500,000 sq metre site for an offshore construction project
Key requirements:
- 15 years of experience - Successful history as a Logistics and Construction Specialist - Experience on Mixed use projects over a billion AED - Have a Consultancy background - Be available to start within 2 weeks
Please send your updated CV to me immediately if you are interested in this high profile opportunity.
If this opportunity is not for you, please pass on to anyone who may be suitable.
